(126, '0524126', 1, 4560, '030AC123C090026', 'Dead Inverter', 'Both the replacement units have been operational when they were installed and all the inverters on the site have resulted in being dead. \r\n\r\nSummary:\r\nSolar link submitted claim on 21/07/2023. Case - G006360 – FAULT – Dead Inverter. Inverter SN: 030AC1201070349. Solis replaced with inverter SN: 130AC2232230049\r\nSolar Link submitted another claim on 31/01/2024. Case - G007170 – FAULT – Dead inverter. SN: 130AC2232230049. Solis replaced inverter with SN: 030AC123C090026\r\nSolar Link submitted another claim on 19/04/2024. Case- G007502- FAULT – Dead Inverter. SN: 030AC123C090026.\r\n\r\nSolis cannot take responsibility for these failures and we cannot provide any further support for this site. \r\n\r\nWe understand and appreciate that you have contracted qualified installers however, repeated failures at this particular site with multiple different inverters confirms there is external factor damaging the inverter.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-05-29 03:45:54', '2024-09-19 12:03:00'),
