(148, '0624148', 1, 6023, 'AL7011023030162', 'PV Generation', 'I have been monitoring my system in relation to PV generation for this month to date.\r\nThe original projection was that my system would generate an average of 10kwh per day for June.\r\nThe reality is substantially short of that.\r\nIn fact today (which was a clear sunny day all day) is the only day that has reached (not exceeded) the projected average.\r\nTo average 10kwh I would have expected the daily results to have maybe been fluctuating from 5 to 15 to achieve the projected 10.\r\nIn fact our winter so far has been very mild, with very few days of deep cloud cover and rain.\r\nThe daily PV has fluctuated between 5 and 9 for the most part, for an average of only 7.\r\nThat might seem close but is in fact an underachievement of 30% which is substantial.\r\n\r\nOn May 30th the PV generation was only 1.9kwh\r\n\r\n\r\nI have attached an excel examination of this month to date, plus a picture showing the kind of day we had and a screenshot showing that at 1.46pm we had only generated 7.6kwh.\r\n\r\nCan you please provide evidence of the two strings daily generation for June?\r\nI am concerned that there is something not right when a perfectly clear sunny day cannot exceed the projected average for the month.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-06-19 23:09:58', '2024-08-05 01:02:54'),
(149, '0624149', 1, 7478, 'R6S3103J2336E27012', 'System Issues', 'The inverter is at it again.  \r\n\r\nIs their any way to get it replaced please.  I can safely say I\'ve lost over $50 to $100 worth of solar generation due to either the inverter or solar panels.  I understand that its been checked but I\'m paying for a faulty system. \r\n\r\nApologies for the consistent emails, but I\'ve had previous systems through solar link so I\'m putting my trust in it too please get this rectified.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-06-20 23:10:11', '2024-09-16 11:40:24'),
(150, '0624150', 1, 3303, NULL, 'Installation Issue', 'The client called to report that, five years after the installation, the old inverter was not functioning because the battery we installed was not communicating with it. To find out the precise state of their system and the contents we installed, more information is required.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-06-24 01:38:08', '2024-07-30 02:19:11'),
