(178, '0724178', 1, 5340, 'AL2002221110097', 'Fault on System', 'Rob called that since the system was installed there\'s a fault showing. \r\nNo internet available. Client advised that he\'ll be back few days from now and call me to troubleshoot the system.', 'low', 'on_hold', 0, 0, 2, '2024-07-22 23:54:28', '2025-05-20 14:17:40'),
