(224, '0924223', 1, 7566, '001XOKF240059B', 'RedX Installation Issue', 'The installation wasn\'t signed off by the inspector because the battery wasn\'t charging. Saj reported that the CT are buzzing and turning to brown. RedX advised that the issue is with the installation but Saj says that it was checked more than couple of times. We requested RedX to send us with their own cable and CT. We are waiting for an update from them.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-09-06 09:18:04', '2024-09-23 14:28:47'),
