(227, '0924227', 1, 7594, 'ALD001122121460 - ALD001122120293', 'System only charging based on the house load when using generator', 'I\'m back again. Unfortunately we\'ve had some heavy cloud cover today and I\'m back to suffering the same issue with the generator not charging the batteries - the inverter is only taking enough energy from the generator to cover the usage load. Can you get in touch with Alpha and see if they can fix it please? \r\nI am currently running the generator as I type.', 'normal', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2024-09-10 12:18:37', '2024-09-12 10:01:07'),
