(326, '0125326', 1, 7410, NULL, 'System Issues', 'I need to start a warranty claim for my Solax X1 Smart inverter as it has been acting very strangely\r\n\r\nThe list of issues are\r\n\r\n- Reporting 0W usage and presumably correct PV generation intermittently\r\n- Reporting in excess of 3-6kw energy being consumed when nothing is on, have tested with breakers turned off for heating/hot water, kitchen circuit, all lighting circuits etc. No change\r\n- Reporting 0 draw from the grid intermittently\r\n- Reporting huge draw from the grid and no PV generation when PV is definitely generating', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-14 15:59:10', '2025-02-26 08:30:54'),
