(329, '0125329', 1, 7637, '3804010246060508', 'Production Limited', 'customer Liz has emailed and called me about their production, they have had their system inspected and said that with the temp being 26 degrees at 11.30 am their system is only producing 80 Watts. \r\n\r\nI have included their login info and some photos- Can you please check this out and update Liz.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-15 09:46:44', '2025-02-26 09:03:59'),
(330, '0125330', 1, 7638, 'H2S3992J2338E05387', 'Power Outages', 'Just confirm that we are experiencing power outages, possibly of about one or two minutes in lengths, once or twice most days.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-15 11:22:41', '2025-05-28 08:54:57'),
(331, '0125331', 1, 1916, 'H3LE05F7186021', 'Battery Discharging Issues', 'over the Xmas period we had occasion to turn on our air-conditioner & it just so happened I had nothing on my to-do-agenda & looked at the Solax power mix & found the Solax battery was only supplying background power & 99.99% of our excess energy need was being drawn from the grid. This is despite the battery being at 98% capacity.\r\n\r\nTwo days later I repeated the same exercise and found that the battery was again virtually switched off & the grid was again supplying 99.99% of our excess energy need, despite being at 98% capacity.\r\n\r\nWhy would the Solax battery switch off when it should have been supplementing the solar input.\r\n\r\nIn the New Year I contacted Solax (Dandenong) and queried why the battery turned itself off & got the following reply today (06 Jan 2025)', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-15 13:31:43', '2025-02-05 13:48:02'),
(332, '0125332', 1, 7253, NULL, 'Wifi connectivity issue', 'Daryl, Kerry said she contacted you December 2023 to help her connect and it isn\'t connected. Please can you contact Kerry Beamish again in Traralgon to help her set the app to her inverter as she still can\'t get it to work. She sent the WIFI extender back to the retailer as it didnt work. Do you have any other suggestions to get the SOFAR App connected to her SOFAR inverter. She has a Powerpal connected to her switchboard which is connected to WIFI and that works well with a strong connection which is in the similar position to where the inverter is.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-15 15:49:34', '2025-01-16 09:47:28'),
(333, '0125333', 1, 5738, NULL, 'UPS Issues', 'Mark Serradura called me regarding his Alpha Smile 5 10.1kWh battery (AC Retrofit) which we installed in June 2022 by Leigh Rochardson. Mark has his number and will call him anyway.\r\n\r\nBasically, when there are grid-outages, the UPS shuts down and he gets no power and his power to the house turns off. He has a UPS which we connected at the time. So, basically, when there are power outages, the UPS shuts down and doesn\'t kick-in and a couple of times, the circuit breaker in which the UPS is connected to, shuts off at the switchboard.\r\n\r\nAnyway, Mark is calling the installer, Leigh Richardson as we provided his details at the time for install and also left Mark his details.\r\n\r\nAddress: 45 Callista street Botanic Ridge Vic\r\nEmail: mksec1@bigpond.com\r\n0427 819 977.\r\n\r\nHe is also interested in getting a new system with us which I have quoted him for. He has an Alpha Smile 5 10.1kwh battery with UPS.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-15 16:15:44', '2025-05-20 09:52:43'),
(334, '0125334', 1, 7639, NULL, 'System Offline', 'We just realised our solar has been off-line for months. We were not aware of this as the notifications on the app were not set up. Can we please get assistance with this as I was under the impression, it would not go offline and we don\'t need to do anything. This is disappointing that we have been off line for months and not one picked up on it.', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-01-16 09:26:04', '2025-03-07 09:41:00'),
