(360, '0225360', 1, 7648, 'R6S3802J2433E44584', 'System Low Production', 'On Monday Michael phoned to advise that the solar system has been inspected by Jacks sign off inspector \r\nAnd if I got it right the solar system is still waiting in a queue to be connected to the grid.\r\n Is this correct ?\r\nHowever he said that any power generated from the solar panels can be used in the home??\r\nWhen I look at my 8kw inverter it only reads 300 down to 0\r\nI would have thought that if it was working then it should be showing 000’s if it was functioning properly \r\nI’m confused, I don’t think it is working \r\nPlease get back to me', 'low', 'resolved', 0, 0, 2, '2025-02-13 13:55:58', '2025-03-03 13:52:07'),
